{"tid":1615733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共已經逐漸進入我地圈套","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:11:56.000Z","uid":62369,"like":410,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7089d0c5ae6218fe35c7160f5eb7fcce771fe5","tid":1615733,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"佢做嘅每一步都係我地革命成功嘅必經階段，<br />\n雖然有手足傷亡同失蹤，我地都非常痛心唔想發生！<br />\n但無可避免呢啲都係必經階段！<br />\n反而港共如果好似之前咁 ，一直由我地嘉年華反而覺得勝算唔高。<br />\n不過依家就算佢採取放任態度都太遲，只會令我地更大發揮。<br />\n依家仲話立反蒙面法，估唔到加速左我地嘅進度，反正遲早會面對，早啲面對早啲贏，老套啲講真係關關難過關關過。<br />\n大家加油，只要我地唔放棄勝利終歸屬於我地！"},{"pid":"ddf5c1676dbd1bc9cdd5e93394e67395ea6f98ea","tid":1615733,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b59243392da0eaf1142ade1720f0c67aa28449","tid":1615733,"uid":62369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"如果我地驚我地放棄點對得住手足！"},{"pid":"5486530065503ecf93a78dc646eda2eee61f4b0f","tid":1615733,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b8748db2779df44724718df7965b6db3a34a3a3","tid":1615733,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"[和理非入]只要有心 人人都係物資站，和理非係時候進化做輔助兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615420</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c46aedd72d0b1d36eb4e22ec7c5ac00122a903a7","tid":1615733,"uid":34714,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:59.000Z","msg":"我地捉緊好大盤棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aad0a30a28eae41925a6b06d0a01898b0fe1237","tid":1615733,"uid":329266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"回帶天琦兄立法會辯論"},{"pid":"25e244f616920358bb32f6a58f86ed09f902d83c","tid":1615733,"ui